snippet.title: EDENS ZERO - Announcement Trailer | Xbox Partner Preview October 2024
snippet.description:
EDENS ZERO is coming to consoles and PC in 2025!
A new fantasy opus from Hiro Mashima! Take off to the stars, and adventure!
---
Hiro Mashima's hit manga, EDENS ZERO, is being adapted as a new Action-RPG!

Relive the story of the manga, and explore an open-world planet as you adventure across the Sakura Cosmos. Put yourself in the action, and experience the thrills and emotion of the story along with your favorite characters.

https://www.xbox.com/games/store/Eden-Zero/9P30BRBKH5DQ
